{"thi-ap20:0.1":"Theriapadana ","thi-ap20:0.2":"Ekuposathikavagga ","thi-ap20:0.3":"Patacaratheriapadana ","thi-ap20:1.1":"“Padumuttaro nama jino, ","thi-ap20:1.2":"sabbadhammana paragu; ","thi-ap20:1.3":"Ito satasahassamhi, ","thi-ap20:1.4":"kappe uppajji nayako. ","thi-ap20:2.1":"Tadaham hamsavatiyam, ","thi-ap20:2.2":"jata setthikule ahum; ","thi-ap20:2.3":"Nanaratanapajjote, ","thi-ap20:2.4":"mahasukhasamappita. ","thi-ap20:3.1":"Upetva tam mahaviram, ","thi-ap20:3.2":"assosim dhammadesanam; ","thi-ap20:3.3":"Tato jatapasadaham, ","thi-ap20:3.4":"upesim saranam jinam. ","thi-ap20:4.1":"Tato vinayadharinam, ","thi-ap20:4.2":"aggam vannesi nayako; ","thi-ap20:4.3":"Bhikkhunim lajjinim tadim, ","thi-ap20:4.4":"kappakappavisaradam. ","thi-ap20:5.1":"Tada muditacittaham, ","thi-ap20:5.2":"tam thanamabhikankhini; ","thi-ap20:5.3":"Nimantetva dasabalam, ","thi-ap20:5.4":"sasangham lokanayakam. ","thi-ap20:6.1":"Bhojayitvana sattaham, ","thi-ap20:6.2":"daditvava ticivaram; ","thi-ap20:6.3":"Nipacca sirasa pade, ","thi-ap20:6.4":"idam vacanamabravim. ","thi-ap20:7.1":"‘Ya taya vannita vira, ","thi-ap20:7.2":"ito atthamake muni; ","thi-ap20:7.3":"Tadisaham bhavissami, ","thi-ap20:7.4":"yadi sijjhati nayaka’. ","thi-ap20:8.1":"Tada avoca mam sattha, ","thi-ap20:8.2":"‘bhadde ma bhayi assasa; ","thi-ap20:8.3":"Anagatamhi addhane, ","thi-ap20:8.4":"lacchase tam manoratham. ","thi-ap20:9.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","thi-ap20:9.2":"okkakakulasambhavo; ","thi-ap20:9.3":"Gotamo nama gottena, ","thi-ap20:9.4":"sattha loke bhavissati. ","thi-ap20:10.1":"Tassa dhammesu dayada, ","thi-ap20:10.2":"orasa dhammanimmita; ","thi-ap20:10.3":"Patacarati namena, ","thi-ap20:10.4":"hessati satthu savika’. ","thi-ap20:11.1":"Tadaham mudita hutva, ","thi-ap20:11.2":"yavajivam tada jinam; ","thi-ap20:11.3":"Mettacitta paricarim, ","thi-ap20:11.4":"sasangham lokanayakam. ","thi-ap20:12.1":"Tena kammena sukatena, ","thi-ap20:12.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","thi-ap20:12.3":"Jahitva manusam deham, ","thi-ap20:12.4":"tavatimsamagacchaham. ","thi-ap20:13.1":"Imamhi bhaddake kappe, ","thi-ap20:13.2":"brahmabandhu mahayaso; ","thi-ap20:13.3":"Kassapo nama gottena, ","thi-ap20:13.4":"uppajji vadatam varo. ","thi-ap20:14.1":"Upatthako mahesissa, ","thi-ap20:14.2":"tada asi narissaro; ","thi-ap20:14.3":"Kasiraja kiki nama, ","thi-ap20:14.4":"baranasipuruttame. ","thi-ap20:15.1":"Tassasim tatiya dhita, ","thi-ap20:15.2":"bhikkhuni iti vissuta; ","thi-ap20:15.3":"Dhammam sutva jinaggassa, ","thi-ap20:15.4":"pabbajjam samarocayim. ","thi-ap20:16.1":"Anujani na no tato, ","thi-ap20:16.2":"agareva tada mayam; ","thi-ap20:16.3":"Visavassasahassani, ","thi-ap20:16.4":"vicarimha atandita. ","thi-ap20:17.1":"Komaribrahmacariyam, ","thi-ap20:17.2":"rajakanna sukhedhita; ","thi-ap20:17.3":"Buddhopatthananirata, ","thi-ap20:17.4":"mudita sattadhitaro. ","thi-ap20:18.1":"Samani samanagutta ca, ","thi-ap20:18.2":"bhikkhuni bhikkhudayika; ","thi-ap20:18.3":"Dhamma ceva sudhamma ca, ","thi-ap20:18.4":"sattami sanghadayika. ","thi-ap20:19.1":"Aham uppalavanna ca, ","thi-ap20:19.2":"khema bhadda ca bhikkhuni; ","thi-ap20:19.3":"Kisagotami dhammadinna, ","thi-ap20:19.4":"visakha hoti sattami. ","thi-ap20:20.1":"Tehi kammehi sukatehi, ","thi-ap20:20.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","thi-ap20:20.3":"Jahitva manusam deham, ","thi-ap20:20.4":"tavatimsamagacchaham. ","thi-ap20:21.1":"Pacchime ca bhave dani, ","thi-ap20:21.2":"jata setthikule aham; ","thi-ap20:21.3":"Savatthiyam puravare, ","thi-ap20:21.4":"iddhe phite mahaddhane. ","thi-ap20:22.1":"Yada ca yobbanupeta, ","thi-ap20:22.2":"vitakkavasaga aham; ","thi-ap20:22.3":"Naram jarapatim disva, ","thi-ap20:22.4":"tena saddhim agacchaham. ","thi-ap20:23.1":"Ekaputtapasutaham, ","thi-ap20:23.2":"dutiyo kucchiya mamam; ","thi-ap20:23.3":"Tadaham matapitaro, ","thi-ap20:23.4":"okkhamiti sunicchita. ","thi-ap20:24.1":"Narocesim patim mayham, ","thi-ap20:24.2":"tada tamhi pavasite; ","thi-ap20:24.3":"Ekika niggata geha, ","thi-ap20:24.4":"gantum savatthimuttamam. ","thi-ap20:25.1":"Tato me sami agantva, ","thi-ap20:25.2":"sambhavesi pathe mamam; ","thi-ap20:25.3":"Tada me kammaja vata, ","thi-ap20:25.4":"uppanna atidaruna. ","thi-ap20:26.1":"Utthito ca mahamegho, ","thi-ap20:26.2":"pasutisamaye mama; ","thi-ap20:26.3":"Dabbatthaya tada gantva, ","thi-ap20:26.4":"sami sappena marito. ","thi-ap20:27.1":"Tada vijatadukkhena, ","thi-ap20:27.2":"anatha kapana aham; ","thi-ap20:27.3":"Kunnadim puritam disva, ","thi-ap20:27.4":"gacchanti sakulalayam. ","thi-ap20:28.1":"Balam adaya atarim, ","thi-ap20:28.2":"parakule ca ekakam; ","thi-ap20:28.3":"Sayetva balakam puttam, ","thi-ap20:28.4":"itaram taranayaham. ","thi-ap20:29.1":"Nivatta ukkuso hasi, ","thi-ap20:29.2":"tarunam vilapantakam; ","thi-ap20:29.3":"Itaranca vahi soto, ","thi-ap20:29.4":"saham sokasamappita. ","thi-ap20:30.1":"Savatthinagaram gantva, ","thi-ap20:30.2":"assosim sajane mate; ","thi-ap20:30.3":"Tada avocam sokatta, ","thi-ap20:30.4":"mahasokasamappita. ","thi-ap20:31.1":"‘Ubho putta kalankata, ","thi-ap20:31.2":"panthe mayham pati mato; ","thi-ap20:31.3":"Mata pita ca bhata ca, ","thi-ap20:31.4":"ekacitamhi dayhare’. ","thi-ap20:32.1":"Tada kisa ca pandu ca, ","thi-ap20:32.2":"anatha dinamanasa; ","thi-ap20:32.3":"Ito tato bhamantiham, ","thi-ap20:32.4":"addasam narasarathim. ","thi-ap20:33.1":"Tato avoca mam sattha, ","thi-ap20:33.2":"‘putte ma soci assasa; ","thi-ap20:33.3":"Attanam te gavesassu, ","thi-ap20:33.4":"kim nirattham vihannasi. ","thi-ap20:34.1":"Na santi putta tanaya, ","thi-ap20:34.2":"na nati napi bandhava; ","thi-ap20:34.3":"Antakenadhipannassa, ","thi-ap20:34.4":"natthi natisu tanata’. ","thi-ap20:35.1":"Tam sutva munino vakyam, ","thi-ap20:35.2":"pathamam phalamajjhagam; ","thi-ap20:35.3":"Pabbajitvana naciram, ","thi-ap20:35.4":"arahattamapapunim. ","thi-ap20:36.1":"Iddhisu ca vasi homi, ","thi-ap20:36.2":"dibbaya sotadhatuya; ","thi-ap20:36.3":"Paracittani janami, ","thi-ap20:36.4":"satthusasanakarika. ","thi-ap20:37.1":"Pubbenivasam janami, ","thi-ap20:37.2":"dibbacakkhu visodhitam; ","thi-ap20:37.3":"Khepetva asave sabbe, ","thi-ap20:37.4":"visuddhasim sunimmala. ","thi-ap20:38.1":"Tatoham vinayam sabbam, ","thi-ap20:38.2":"santike sabbadassino; ","thi-ap20:38.3":"Uggahim sabbavittharam, ","thi-ap20:38.4":"byaharinca yathatatham. ","thi-ap20:39.1":"Jino tasmim gune tuttho, ","thi-ap20:39.2":"etadagge thapesi mam; ","thi-ap20:39.3":"‘Agga vinayadharinam, ","thi-ap20:39.4":"patacarava ekika’. ","thi-ap20:40.1":"Paricinno maya sattha, ","thi-ap20:40.2":"katam buddhassa sasanam; ","thi-ap20:40.3":"Ohito garuko bharo, ","thi-ap20:40.4":"bhavanetti samuhata. ","thi-ap20:41.1":"Yassatthaya pabbajita, ","thi-ap20:41.2":"agarasmanagariyam; ","thi-ap20:41.3":"So me attho anuppatto, ","thi-ap20:41.4":"sabbasamyojanakkhayo. ","thi-ap20:42.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","thi-ap20:42.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap20:42.3":"viharami anasava. ","thi-ap20:43.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","thi-ap20:43.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap20:43.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","thi-ap20:44.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","thi-ap20:44.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap20:44.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","thi-ap20:45.1":"Ittham sudam patacara bhikkhuni ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","thi-ap20:46.1":"Patacaratheriyapadanam dasamam. ","thi-ap20:47.1":"Ekuposathikavaggo dutiyo. ","thi-ap20:48.1":"Tassuddanam ","thi-ap20:49.1":"Ekuposathika ceva, ","thi-ap20:49.2":"salala catha modaka; ","thi-ap20:49.3":"Ekasana pancadipa, ","thi-ap20:49.4":"nalamali ca gotami. ","thi-ap20:50.1":"Khema uppalavanna ca, ","thi-ap20:50.2":"patacara ca bhikkhuni; ","thi-ap20:50.3":"Gatha satani panceva, ","thi-ap20:50.4":"nava capi taduttari. "}